      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(status): add gateway delivery health telemetry",
        "body": "## Summary\n- surface generic channel runtime warnings for disconnected, stale, stuck, and restart-pending states\n- add inbound delivery telemetry for received, dispatch started/completed, session turn created, and processed events\n- show delivery counters, transport liveness, multi-gateway listener warnings, and no-recent-agent-activity warnings in status output\n- normalize provider allowlist catalog-loading flags accepted from plugin auth prompts\n\nFixes #49577\n\n## Tests\n- `corepack pnpm test -- src/auto-reply/reply/dispatch-from-config.test.ts src/auto-reply/dispatch.test.ts extensions/diagnostics-prometheus/src/service.test.ts extensions/diagnostics-otel/src/service.test.ts src/infra/channels-status-issues.test.ts src/commands/status-all/diagnosis.test.ts src/commands/status-all/report-lines.test.ts src/logging/diagnostic-stability.test.ts test/scripts/parallels-smoke-model.test.ts src/plugins/provider-validation.test.ts src/commands/channels.surfaces-signal-runtime-errors-channels-status-output.test.ts` - passed 8 Vitest shards in 29.58s\n- `corepack pnpm exec oxfmt --check src/auto-reply/reply/dispatch-from-config.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/dispatch-from-config.ts test/scripts/parallels-smoke-model.test.ts src/plugins/provider-validation.ts extensions/diagnostics-prometheus/src/service.ts extensions/diagnostics-otel/src/service.ts CHANGELOG.md`\n- `git diff --check upstream/main...HEAD`\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- Behavior or issue addressed: connected gateway inbound delivery now records payload-safe delivery diagnostics and exposes them through the `diagnostics.stability` Gateway RPC used by status diagnostics.\n- Real environment tested: local macOS 26.4.1 arm64 checkout, isolated `pr72724` OpenClaw profile, local loopback gateway on `ws://127.0.0.1:19724`.\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch:\n  - Started a real local gateway from the PR branch: `corepack pnpm openclaw --profile pr72724 gateway run --port 19724 --bind loopback --allow-unconfigured --auth token --token <redacted>`\n  - Approved the isolated profile's local CLI device for the requested operator write scope.\n  - Sent a real WebChat inbound delivery through the gateway: `corepack pnpm openclaw --profile pr72724 gateway call chat.send --url ws://127.0.0.1:19724 --token <redacted> --json --timeout 15000 --params '{\"sessionKey\":\"main\",\"message\":\"Reply exactly OK.\",\"idempotencyKey\":\"pr72724-proof-4\",\"timeoutMs\":1000}'`\n  - Queried live stability diagnostics: `corepack pnpm openclaw --profile pr72724 gateway stability --url ws://127.0.0.1:19724 --token <redacted> --json`\n\n- Evidence after fix: redacted terminal excerpts from the connected local gateway run:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"runId\": \"pr72724-proof-4\",\n  \"status\": \"started\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"message.received\",\n  \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n  \"source\": \"dispatchInboundMessage\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"message.dispatch.started\",\n  \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n  \"source\": \"replyResolver\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"byType\": {\n      \"message.received\": 1,\n      \"message.queued\": 1,\n      \"session.state\": 1,\n      \"message.dispatch.started\": 1\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n- Observed result after fix: a connected gateway/channel inbound path accepted `chat.send`, returned a started run id, and the live `diagnostics.stability` RPC reported the new payload-free `message.received` and dispatch telemetry events from the inbound dispatch boundary.\n- What was not tested: external Discord/Signal/Telegram live transport delivery; this proof uses the connected built-in WebChat channel path on a local gateway.\n",
        "branch": "fix/49577-gateway-status-process-warning",
